<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      body {
        background: url("../images/background.jpg");
      }

      #animate {
        animation-name: change-colour;
        animation-duration: 7s;
        animation-iteration-count: infinite;
      }

      @keyframes change-colour {
        50% {
          color: crimson;
        }
      }
    </style>

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>
  <body
    class="
      container-fluid
      d-flex
      flex-column
      align-items-center
      bg-dark
      text-light
    "
  >
    <%- include('common/nav', { page: '/about' } ) %>
    <div class="px-md-5 mb-4 fs-5 text-center" style="margin-top: 70px">
      <i
        >When I find myself in times of trouble, Mother Mary comes to me
        <br />
        Speaking words of wisdom: "<strong id="animate">Ball is life</strong
        >"</i
      >
    </div>
    <div class="card bg-secondary mx-md-5 mb-3" style="opacity: 0.9">
      <h6 class="card-header">What is Ball is Life?</h6>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>
          <strong>Ball is Life</strong> is a community for NBA fans to stay
          updated on the latest and follow games live, while pitting against
          each other to see who's the best at predicting game outcomes.
        </p>

        <p>
          Everyday at 3pm SGT, users can submit predictions for the next day's
          games. Predictions will close at 12am SGT.
        </p>

        <p>
          The next day at 3pm after the games have been played, predictions will
          be tallied and the leaderboard updated. Become the top predictor!
        </p>

        <p>
          Game threads lets you stay close to the action and post instant
          reactions to whatever is happening. Not good enough? Join the live
          chat to interact real-time with other fans watching the game!
        </p>

        <p>Sign up today to be a part of the Ball is Life philosophy!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
